::You snap back to reality &mdash; this is the Grove of Epiphany. Even though it's not your first time here, the scenery before you still manages to leave you speechless in awe.
::You still remember that you came here to pursue that distant voice.
::"{{MC|f=Young lady|m=Young man}}, do you desire wisdom?"
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} That's it! This voice!
:::'''Calidorthos:''' Come. I shall bestow upon you the greatest treasure of the Grove.
:::A ghost!
:::'''Calidorthos:''' Hey! Watch your tongue, young one.
:::I desire Stellar Jades.
