::{{DIcon|Arrow}} I desire Stellar Jades.
::'''Calidorthos:''' Alas, there's no wealth to be here, though there is something much more precious &mdash; knowledge.
::'''Calidorthos:''' I am a strand of consciousness left behind by the Great Sage Calidorthos to manage this grand library, known as the Index.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Isn't that just a ghost?
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Got. A digital lifeform then.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Got anything in here that's adult-only?
