::'''Calidorthos:''' Through {{Rubi|Cerces'|Reason Titan}} roots and {{Rubi|Mnestia's|Romance Titan}} golden threads, this wisdom has been able to extend outward, enveloping every corner of the Grove, interwoven into a network that bears knowledge.
