::'''Calidorthos:''' But perseverance rewards the steadfast. In the end, I have found a successor to whom I can entrust this place.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} You've got a keen eye.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Who're you talking about?
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} I'm not it. Stop spouting nonsense.
